Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take the old bag to Kaido-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Tension Rises in Onigashima!\NTwo Emperors of the Sea Meet?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:49.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,EBISU TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take it upon myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...to lay Yasuie-sama's body\Nto rest in Kuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take extra care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe a great debt to Yasuie-sama, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There is another thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I want to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About the flyer with the symbol\Nthat went around recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been 20 years\Nsince the name Kozuki perished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I cannot gather enough soldiers\Nto seek my revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel bad about the Kozuki Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made the flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The symbol does not mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...just a prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Orochi was a bigger coward than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He got flustered and jailed the innocents\Nwho had the moon tattoo which was a popular design!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Yasuie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fill you with bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to recite the curse\Nthat binds your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"A man of such small caliber...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...shall never know the taste of oden\Nfor as long as he shall live!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.81,OS,,0,0,0,,A MAN OF SUCH SMALL CALIBER SHALL NEVER KNOW\NTHE TASTE OF ODEN FOR AS LONG AS HE SHALL LIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Yasuie-sama,\Nour long-cherished wish has not been crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot have a massive funeral,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but we at least want to lay him to rest\Nin the same ground as Oden-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--Please!\N--Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nami! Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me! Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe travels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:36.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,LAND OF WANO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At a dock on the way from the Flower Capital to Kuri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:40.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,WANTED
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,USOHACHI      OROBI      PENGUIN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At this very moment, to catch the serious criminals\Nwho tried to kill Orochi-sama and run,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,NAMI THE {\i1}KUNOICHI{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,FRANOSUKE THE CARPENTER     SHACHI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we've set up checkpoints\Nall around the Flower Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, show your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that they wouldn't let us get away\Nso easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We must take that boat\Nif we wanna go to Kuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to come up with a plan\Nto pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,USOHACHI   OROBI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-They're haunted by a ghost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can pass through...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Otoko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be exhausted from crying,\Nshe's sleeping in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI don't know what to say to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonekichi, I'll take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no body warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:16.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,SOUTHWEST PART OF KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a while since the last time\Nwe walked side by side like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just days ago to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is there to see at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something that I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm speechless! Ashura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They need to be fixed up a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I brought them here from\Nports across the country that were destroyed by Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have enough to transport\Nthousands of warriors to Onigashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are quite dependable!\NMy opinion of you has improved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, mine, too.\NYou were not so attentive before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not spend 20 years sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ask Franosuke-dono to do maintenance later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a long, tough road\Nto get to this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But the day of the raid is within our sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,EXCAVATION LABOR CAMP, UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You still need to be resting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's preparing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to master that technique, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ryuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need intensive training,\NI'll be your sparring partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit me without holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow Haki to flow... inside my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Ryuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, the straw hat man...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...certainly used Ryuo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I assume that Kawamatsu the kappa is so strong...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...because he uses Ryuo so well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once the straw hat man masters it,\NI am sure it will help him in the fight against Kaido.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,RINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot believe it took years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...just to get some ordinary deep-fried tofu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot possibly think that\Nthat one is still waiting for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You did not learn anything and you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time,\Nwe had some unwanted interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you don't like leaving it unsettled, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will have the rest of your swords, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Two-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,720-Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more weapons than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy or an ally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you ripping off weapons\Nfrom people who cross the bridge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your life over a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zorojuro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not give it back to you!\NI will give you any sword but that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword Shusui that you had was\Nthe Land of Wano's stolen treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Shusui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When it was taken away,\Nthe whole tragedy began!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,\Nour God of the Blade became enraged,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and each region was defeated one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the country was taken over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What god?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You blasphemer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are a samurai and a monk fighting for\Nin the remote countryside like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It is funny that both of you have\Nno intention of killing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A Fish-Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawa... matsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamatsu?! Is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,ONIGASHIMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You did such a crappy job! Damn you, King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I knocked the ship off of the waterfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Queen, why did you bring her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! What could I do\Nin Udon where communication was cut off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to forget what you did to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so why don't you join us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We have all kinds of people living in our country\Nexcept for three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them might have dwindled and disappeared\Nover time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you uncuff me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "then"?!\NWe won't, you old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How inflexible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, Big Mom and Kaido-sama were\Nmembers of the same pirate group!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncuff her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally here, Linlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! He told you to uncuff me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, he must be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncuff her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you for decades...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Napoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you're back to your usual self!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shy with strangers,\Nso I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'd kill you if you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of fool would march to their own death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the bosses of the underworld on his side,\NLuffy gets all fired up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Kawamatsu and Hiyori finally see each other again,\Nbut Orochi's army comes to attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Swords flash! Zoro and Kawamatsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With their strong determination to protect Hiyori,\NThey brandish their precious swords!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Hiyori's Confession! A Reunion at Bandit's Bridge!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:49.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,